ing: 2 medium zucchinis, cut into thin strips
des: "Zucchini and onions are stir fried with sesame seeds and teriyaki and soy sauces."
ins: Warm the oil in a large skillet over medium heat. Stir in onions, and cook 5 minutes. Add zucchini, and cook, stirring, about 1 minute. Stir in teriyaki sauce, soy sauce, and sesame seeds. Cook until zucchini are tender, about 5 minutes. Stir in ground pepper, and serve immediately.
